<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NURUL HIDAYAH SCHOOL</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --ibm-blue: #0f62fe;
            --ibm-black: #161616;
            --ibm-gray: #f4f4f4;
            --text-main: #393939;
            --shadow-pop: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: var(--text-main);
            background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1600 900"><defs><linearGradient id="grad1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:%23001a4d;stop-opacity:1" /><stop offset="25%" style="stop-color:%23003d99;stop-opacity:1" /><stop offset="50%" style="stop-color:%239933ff;stop-opacity:1" /><stop offset="75%" style="stop-color:%23ff6b99;stop-opacity:1" /><stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:%23ffaa00;stop-opacity:1" /></linearGradient></defs><rect width="1600" height="900" fill="url(%23grad1)"/></svg>');
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(255, 100, 150, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 20%, rgba(255, 200, 50, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 25px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3.8rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--ibm-black);
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f62fe, #ff6b99);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 3vw, 1.3rem);
            color: var(--ibm-blue);
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* EFEK MENONJOL (POP-OUT) */
        .pop-effect {
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid #efefef;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .pop-effect:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-pop);
            border-color: var(--ibm-blue);
            z-index: 20;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        }

        /* MODAL LIGHTBOX */
        .lightbox {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1000;
            padding-top: 50px;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: auto;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                backdrop-filter: blur(0px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            }
        }

        .lightbox.active {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-top: 0;
        }

        .lightbox-content {
            position: relative;
            background-color: transparent;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 0;
            width: 90vw;
            max-width: 900px;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 90vh;
            animation: slideUp 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                transform: scale(0.5) translateY(50px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .lightbox-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .close-lightbox {
            position: absolute;
            top: -40px;
            right: 0;
            color: #f1f1f1;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .close-lightbox:hover,
        .close-lightbox:focus {
            color: #bbb;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        /* 3 BINGKAI DOKUMENTASI UTAMA */
        .hero-gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 35px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .frame-large {
            width: 100%;
            height: clamp(300px, 50vh, 600px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
        }

        .frame-large:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .frame-large img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .frame-large p {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
            color: #999;
            position: absolute;
        }

        /* MATRIX 12 BINGKAI (6 ATAS, 6 BAWAH) */
        .matrix-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 100px 0;
        }

        .frame-medium {
            aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.2;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            border-radius: 2px;
            min-height: 150px;
            cursor: pointer;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .frame-medium:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.3);
        }

        .frame-medium img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* VISI MISI SECTION */
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 6vw, 2.8rem);
            margin: 80px 0 50px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ibm-blue);
            display: block;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .visi-misi-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .kolom-teks {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
        }

        .kolom-teks h3 {
            color: var(--ibm-blue);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--ibm-blue);
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 35px 0 25px;
            font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 4vw, 1.8rem);
        }

        .kolom-teks h4 {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
            margin: 25px 0 12px;
            color: var(--ibm-black);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .kolom-teks p {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            text-align: justify;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .kolom-teks ul {
            padding-left: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .kolom-teks ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        }

        /* GURU GRID (BULAT BESAR PROFESIONAL) */
        .guru-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: clamp(30px, 5vw, 60px);
            margin: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .guru-card {
            position: relative;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .guru-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.3);
        }

        .guru-card img {
            width: clamp(120px, 20vw, 240px);
            height: clamp(120px, 20vw, 240px);
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--ibm-gray);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 4px solid #f0f0f0;
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: block;
        }

        .guru-card:hover img {
            border-color: var(--ibm-blue);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-pop);
        }

        .guru-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem);
            display: block;
            color: var(--ibm-black);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .guru-role {
            font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.8vw, 0.95rem);
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* SEJARAH */
        .history-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: clamp(40px, 8vw, 70px);
            margin-top: 100px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 8px solid var(--ibm-blue);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
        }

        .founder-container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .founder-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: clamp(300px, 40vh, 500px);
            background: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
        }

        .founder-frame img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .founder-frame:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .founder-container p {
            font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2.5vw, 1.1rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--ibm-black);
        }

        .history-text {
            font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
            text-align: justify;
            align-self: center;
            line-height: 2;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* ANIMASI SCROLL */
        .animate-on-scroll {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(50px);
            transition: all 1s ease-out;
        }

        .animate-on-scroll.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE DESIGN */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }

            header {
                padding: 40px 15px;
            }

            .matrix-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
                gap: 15px;
                margin: 60px 0;
            }

            .visi-misi-grid {
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .guru-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
                gap: clamp(20px, 5vw, 40px);
                margin: 60px 0;
            }

            .history-section {
                padding: 30px 20px;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .hero-gallery {
                gap: 20px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }

            .close-lightbox {
                top: -35px;
                font-size: 32px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px 10px;
            }

            header {
                padding: 30px 10px;
            }

            .matrix-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(100px, 1fr));
                gap: 12px;
                margin: 40px 0;
            }

            .frame-large {
                height: clamp(200px, 40vh, 400px);
            }

            .frame-large p {
                font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 2vw, 1.1rem);
            }

            .guru-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: clamp(15px, 4vw, 30px);
            }

            .guru-card img {
                width: clamp(80px, 18vw, 150px);
                height: clamp(80px, 18vw, 150px);
            }

            .visi-misi-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .history-section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding: 20px 15px;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .section-title {
                margin: 50px 0 30px;
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .kolom-teks h3 {
                margin: 20px 0 15px;
            }

            .history-text {
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .lightbox-content {
                width: 95vw;
                max-height: 85vh;
            }

            .close-lightbox {
                top: -30px;
                font-size: 28px;
                width: 40px;
                height: 40px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LIGHTBOX MODAL -->
<div id="lightbox" class="lightbox">
    <div class="lightbox-content">
        <span class="close-lightbox">&times;</span>
        <img id="lightbox-img" class="lightbox-img" src="" alt="Gambar Diperbesar">
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <header class="animate-on-scroll">
        <h1>NURUL HIDAYAH</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Pendidikan Berbasis Agama Islam, Formal, seni & Teknologi</div>
    </header>

    <!-- 3 BINGKAI DOKUMENTASI BESAR UTAMA -->
    <section class="hero-gallery">
        <div class="frame-large pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <p>DOKUMENTASI UTAMA 1</p>
            <img src="" alt="Dokumentasi 1" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-large pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <p>DOKUMENTASI UTAMA 2</p>
            <img src="" alt="Dokumentasi 2" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-large pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <p>DOKUMENTASI UTAMA 3</p>
            <img src="" alt="Dokumentasi 3" style="display: none;">
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MATRIX 12 BINGKAI SEDANG (6 ATAS, 6 BAWAH) -->
    <div class="matrix-grid">
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 1" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 2" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 3" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 4" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 5" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 6" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 7" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 8" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 9" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 10" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 11" style="display: none;">
        </div>
        <div class="frame-medium pop-effect animate-on-scroll" onclick="openLightbox(this.querySelector('img') ? this.querySelector('img').src : '')">
            <img src="" alt="Galeri 12" style="display: none;">
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- VISI & MISI -->
    <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">VISI & MISI</h2>
    <section class="visi-misi-grid animate-on-scroll">

        <!-- KOLOM 1: KB NURUL HIDAYAH -->
        <div class="kolom-teks">
            <h3>1. Sekolah KB NURUL HIDAYAH</h3>
            <p><strong>Lembaga kelompok bermain paud:</strong> "Membentuk generasi Rabbani yang unggul, berakhlak mulia, dan adaptif terhadap perkembangan teknologi sejak usia dini."</p>
            <p>"Menyelenggarakan pendidikan holistik yang mengintegrasikan nilai-nilai Tauhid dengan literasi digital dan seni dasar guna membekali anak menghadapi tantangan perkembangan zaman."</p>

            <h4>Deskripsi Program Pembelajaran (Modern & Inovatif)</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Pendidikan Agama Islam (PAI):</strong> Internalisasi nilai-nilai Islami dan pembiasaan akhlakul karimah melalui metode fun learning yang relevan dengan perkembangan zaman.</li>
                <li><strong>Pengenalan Teknologi:</strong> Pemanfaatan Multimedia Interaktif sebagai media stimulasi kognitif dan pengenalan literasi digital yang aman serta edukatif bagi anak.</li>
                <li><strong>Metode Gabungan:</strong> Implementasi kurikulum berbasis TIK untuk memvisualisasikan konsep-konsep spiritual yang abstrak beserta gabungan ksesinian menjadikan pengalaman belajar yang konkret dan menyenangkan.</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Profil Pendidik TK (Profesionalitas)</h4>
            <p>"Menjadi pendidik PAUD yang kompeten dan berdedikasi dalam mensinergikan kecerdasan intelektual, emosional, dan spiritual anak melalui pendekatan teknologi yang tepat guna."</p>
            <p>"Berkomitmen menjalankan peran sebagai fasilitator yang mengedepankan pendidikan formal keteladanan Islami kesenian sekaligus terbuka terhadap inovasi digital dalam proses pengasuhan dan pengajaran."</p>

            <h4>Pilar Pengembangan</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Pendidikan Karakter:</strong> Menanamkan nilai agama dan budi pekerti luhur.</li>
                <li><strong>Pengembangan Holistik:</strong> Mengoptimalkan kognitif, bahasa, fisik motorik, dan sosial-emosional.</li>
                <li><strong>Pembelajaran Aktif:</strong> Menggunakan metode PAKEM yang menyenangkan.</li>
                <li><strong>Lingkungan Kondusif:</strong> Lingkungan aman, nyaman, dan ramah anak.</li>
                <li><strong>Kemitraan:</strong> Kerjasama harmonis antara sekolah dan orang tua.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- KOLOM 2: SEKOLAH KEAGAMAAN -->
        <div class="kolom-teks">
            <h3>2. Sekolah Keagamaan DINIYAH TAKMILIYAH NURUL HIDAYAH</h3>
            <p><strong>Sekolah Madrasah Diniyah:</strong> Fokus pada Akademik dan Kurikulum Keislaman Tarbiyah, Ta'lim, Ta'dib dan seni sebagai dasar pengajaran adab serta akhlak.</p>
            <p><strong>Madrasah Diniyah Takmiliyah Nurul Hidayah:</strong> Pusat pendidikan keagamaan intensif.</p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>PAI (Pendidikan Agama Islam):</strong> Menjadi pilar kurikulum utama sekolah.</li>
                <li><strong>Ulumuddin:</strong> Penguasaan disiplin ilmu agama secara mendalam dan terstruktur.</li>
                <li><strong>Islamic Environment:</strong> Menciptakan ekosistem belajar yang mendukung nilai-nilai Islam.</li>
                <li><strong>Rahmatan lil 'Alamiin:</strong> Mewujudkan pendidikan Islam yang membawa kedamaian bagi semesta.</li>
                <li><strong>Character Development:</strong> Fokus utama pada pembentukan karakter tangguh setiap peserta didik.</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Kompetensi Profesional Pendidik</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Pedagogik:</strong> Keterampilan mengajar secara efektif dan modern.</li>
                <li><strong>Profesional Keilmuan:</strong> Penguasaan materi agama secara mendalam dan komprehensif.</li>
                <li><strong>Akhlakul Karimah:</strong> Karakter mulia yang menjadi teladan (uswah) bagi murid.</li>
                <li><strong>Integritas & Tanggung Jawab:</strong> Profesionalisme tinggi berbasis nilai keislaman.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 8 GURU (BULAT BESAR PROFESIONAL) -->
    <section class="guru-grid">
        <div class="guru-card animate-on-scroll">
